# Workspace

Two apps: `nextjs-simonask.io` (public site) and `studio-simonask.io` (Sanity Studio).

- Code ships via Git: `staging` → stage.simonask.io, `main` → simonask.io
- Content ships via Sanity publish → webhook revalidates Next.js
- Never commit secrets; use `.env.example` as reference

Before large or cross-app changes, check `memories/INDEX.md` and read at most one relevant file under `memories/`.

Operational runbooks: root `README.md`. Router: root `AGENTS.md`.
